Classes
--------

Collective Variable and Bias Potentials:

class ColVar              collective variable for hybrid (no derivatives)
class MdColVar            collective variable for md (with derivatives)

class CvPotential         colvar bias potential, with 1D derivatives
class CvGridPotential     potential defined on a grid
class CvHarmonicPotential harmonic (umbrella sampling) cv potential

Commands:

class Command
class CvMdSimulateComd   simulate command for cv biased md simulation
class CvHdSimulateComd   simulate command for cv biased hybrid simulation

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
class ColVar {
   void compute() = 0;
   double value();
   void unset();
   bool isSet() const;
}

class MdColvar : public Colvar {
   void addForces(double dPotentialdCv);
}

class CvPotential {
   double value(double colvar);
   double derivative(double colvar);
}
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
